body_html:
Creating an account on Gerrit was not too difficult. I followed the instructions here: https://tensorflow-review.googlesource.com/#/c/1061/2/CONTRIBUTING.md

If that is the only requirement for going through the contribution flow, then I'd recommend giving it a shot.
